# AppExtensionPoint.Capability

**Protocol**

An interface that marks a type as an extension capability.

## Declaration

```swift
protocol Capability : Identifiable
```

## Overview

Types adopt this protocol if they comprise part of an extension’s capabilities.

## Inherits From

- Identifiable
